to the editor re refusing to recant keating resigns as church panel chief news article june 17 frank keating compared the silence of the catholic hierarchy to the silence of la cosa nostra he is not alone in feeling this way many catholics have felt for a long time that the church is a closed organization run by a select group committed to secrecy which has often done great harm to the church the time for diplomacy is over mr keating should be commended for telling the cutting truth which sets people free and calls attention to what is going on john j mccabe latham ny june 17 2003

